com.mnnit.tutorspoint.core

Class UserBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mnnit.tutorspoint.core.UserBuilder

  • public class UserBuilder
extends java.lang.Object
    A builder class for the User class.
    A user can be built with createUser() method after calling setUsername(String) or/and setPassword(String)

    For example,

    User user = new UserBuilder().setUsername("foo").setPassword("bar").createUser();
